    About this item

    • AMOLED Screen Always-on Display: niolina smart watches for women features a delicate 1.19 inch high-definition AMOLED touch screen with a resolution of 390 * 390. The integration of AMOLED technology not only improves screen energy efficiency, but also ensures a wider viewing angle, ensuring clear visibility under any lighting conditions. Always-on display function can display 24/7, so you can easily read time and other information. You can activate this feature in the watch's settings and customize the desired always display type.
    • Smartwatch with Messages and Calls: The ladies round smart watch adopts the latest bluetooth 5.2 technology, which can achieve fast and stable connections. Equipped with built-in speakers and microphones, you can make and answer calls directly on your smart watch. Calls and notifications (Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram, Twitter) displayed on the smartwatch directly (no reply message function). The watch will vibrate once receive a message, so it will not miss any important calls or messages even during work or exercise.
    • Smart Watch Monitors Your Health: The perfect smart watch women provide truly comprehensive health protection, with health monitoring functions (heart rate/blood pressure/blood oxygen/sleep) to better detect and analyze your health status (This data is for reference only, not for medical reference). Women's smartwatch can also record a woman's menstrual period for thoughtful menstrual management. You can also receive drinking water and sedentary reminders to help you rationalize your lifestyle.
    • Smartwatch with Multiple Sport Modes: The women's fitness tracker supports multiple sports modes (walking, running, hiking, cycling, basketball, etc.) automatically monitors and records daily steps, exercise time and calorie consumption in real time, and synchronizes them to the App. Help you establish good exercise habits and a more positive lifestyle.
    • Two Straps and Multi Style Dial: With the FitCloudPro App, you can easily control your smartwatch. The application offers a variety of personalized dial wallpapers for you to choose from, and you can also customize the watch face with your favorite photos. The womens smart watches is equipped with two styles strap: stainless steel strap and skin friendly silicone strap. Whether it's for fitness or work, it can switch between fashion and leisure, meeting various matching needs.
    • Android and IOS Smartwatch: Compatible with most Android and iOS phones (Android 5.0+, iOS 10.0+, Bluetooth 5.0+). The smart watch for android phones is equipped with a powerful 170mAh battery. It only takes 2 hours to fully charge, providing up to 5 days of working time and 30 days of standby time. IP68 waterproof, no longer worried about washing hands and rainy days. If you have any questions with our smart watch, please contact us. We will provide you with satisfactory after-sales service.

        How to Connect Your Smartwatch with Your Phones?

        Please kindly noted below tips for your quick start:

        1. Turn on your phone's bluetooth and location;

        2. Download the FitCloudPro APP;

        3. Open the APP and select the device;

        4. Find the corresponding watch to connect;

        5. After the APP bluetooth connection is successful, wait a few seconds to pair the call bluetooth;

        6. After the pairing is successful, you can make and receive calls.

        Notice:

        1. Please fully charge before use it.

        2.When the watch is connected to the "FitCloudPro" App, if you need to turn on various message reminders, you need to manually open each item and keep the app running in the background.

            How customer reviews and ratings work

            Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

            Sie erscheint in natura wie auf den Produktfotos abgebildet, ist sauber verarbeitet, wirkt leicht, aber nicht gerade flach.
            Die beiden Armbnder, silbern aus Edelstal und lachsfarben aus Silikon, kommen weich, biegsam und ausreichend lang daher. Der Armband-Wechsel bereitet keine greren Probleme.
            Im Gesamten trgt sich die Uhr angenehm und strt nicht.

            Das Display zeigt sich klar und deutlich und kann bei schlechten Lichtverhltnissen problemlos abgelesen werden. Unterschiedliche Ziffernbltter stehen in der App zur Auswahl bereit. Wem keines zusagt, kann sich sein eigenes kreieren.

            Die Kopplung der Watch mit dem Samsung-Smartphone, fr die man die "FitCloudPro" App bentigt, hat auf Anhieb geklappt. Die Verbindung bleibt stabil.

            Die wasserdichte Uhr arbeitet recht zuverlssig. Ergebnisse von Trackings unzhliger Sportarten, Schrittzhler, Herzfrequenz- und Blutdruckmessung stellen sich im Vergleich als stimmig heraus. Benachrichtigungen jeglicher Art erfolgen prompt. Telefonieren sowie Musik steuern bereiten keinerlei Probleme. Der Sprachassistent macht seinen Job.
